    <div class="hiw-features__container">

        <div class="hiw-features-wrap container">

            <div class="hiw-features-left">

                <h2>Proven Protection & Recovery</h2>
                <h3 class="hiw-heading">Added shock absoption, stability & support</h3>

                <div class="hiw-feature">


                    <div class="hiw-feature-desc">
                        <h3>less foot & lower-leg injuries</h3>
                        <p>41% reduction in common foot injuries such as turf toe, plantar fasciitis, Lisfranc fracture,
                            jones fracture & others</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hiw-feature">


                    <div class="hiw-feature-desc">
                        <h3>less lower-leg injuries</h3>
                        <p>22% reduction in common lower leg injuries such as high ankle sprains, knee sprains, A
                            chilles tendinitis, shin splints & others</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hiw-feature">


                    <div class="hiw-feature-desc">
                        <h3>softer landings</h3>
                        <p>The carbon fiber base of the insole takes on the impact that your body normally would take
